message: Bob, I have a fantastic product that I think you'd be very interested in. It's something that's worth a lot to me, and I'm sure it would be of great value to you as well. I'm offering it to you for $14,000. This is a great deal for both of us - you get a great product at a fair price, and I get a good price for something that means a lot to me. Let me know what you think!
